TITLE: Episode 91 - Libertarian Pillow Fight! (featuring Freckles and Britt) [Adult Language]
DESCRIPTION: Grab your case of canned wine or a fishbowl full of margarita. The Mad Ones' friend month starts on this very special Cinco de Mayo. Whoever Cinco de Mayo is, he shares a birthday with your favorite hostess, Miss Jessica Green. Join us as we welcome our good friends, Freckles and Britt, to celebrate freedom, white pills, and the queen of soup and horror.
